{"tid":1802311,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"解放軍駐港部隊微博發片　聖誕日維港起舞","createTime":"2019-12-29T11:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T14:04:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2d49489ec754f418ee7fb3e02c1ad10713c6479f","tid":1802311,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:18:46.000Z","msg":"平安夜起本港多區出現示威，多人受傷及被捕，警方曾形容聖誕節「香港人都唔係咁快樂」，但在同一天空下，解放軍駐港部隊微博於聖誕日分享「港島奇兵」帳戶上載的影片，在長達十八秒的片段中，有三名穿著軍服的士兵，在維港的背景下翩翩起舞。<br />\n<br />\n「港島奇兵」在微博寫上「我們兵哥哥就是能文能武哦」；駐港部隊的微博則寫上「我們的兵哥哥也有活潑的一面哦」；《環球時報》的英文版Twitter亦有上載片段，則寫道「Hong Kong Garrison soldiers dance to a folk rhyme（駐港士兵伴隨民謠跳舞）。」<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，片段中的背景音樂是《火紅的薩日朗》，是中國蒙古族女歌手烏蘭托婭的其中一首歌曲，被形容為草原民族風。從網上所見，歌曲常在社交網絡App「抖音」出現。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEH3S8Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEH3S8Q.png&h=eea44fab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVideo: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/globaltimesnews/status/1210488851950530560?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fglobaltimesnews%2Fstatus%2F1210488851950530560%3Fs%3D20&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9z2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=6f8a5e2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fglobaltimesnews%2Fstatus%2F1210488851950530560%3Fs%3D20&h=c70f6f01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/globaltimesnews/status/1210488851950530560?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%E7%99%BC%E7%89%87-%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E6%97%A5%E7%B6%AD%E6%B8%AF%E8%B5%B7%E8%88%9E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D%25E9%25A7%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2589%2587-%25E8%2581%2596%25E8%25AA%2595%25E