T12:41:01.000Z","msg":"真係睇到堅想作嘔，群魔亂舞"},{"pid":"af880e66318badd8e71431b68c168375ea962f27","tid":1802311,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:41:29.000Z","msg":"突發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZuNAtv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZuNAtv.png&h=a8f19de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不反都出埋唔好再搵藉口唔出<br />\n1月1號維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n【元旦大遊行　不反已出】<br />\n<br />\n民陣已收到警方發出的不反對通知書，<br />\n可以正式同各位講多次，1.1 維園見！<br />\n<br />\n元旦遊行當日將會有超過 40 個新成立工會同大家見面，歡迎大家了解詳情，加入你所屬行業的工會，壯大抗爭的組織力量。<br />\n<br />\n毋忘承諾，並肩同行，五大訴求，缺一不可，<br />\n一月一，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n【民陣元旦大遊行】<br />\n2020.1.1 星期三 Wednesday｜2PM<br />\n維園中央草坪 遊行至 遮打道行人專用區<br />\nFrom Victoria Park (Central Lawn) to <br />\nChater Road Pedestrian Precinct<br />\n<br />\n*已取得不反對通知書<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Received<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ec3npyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fec3npyj.jpg&h=648ef6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認住831幫警甴殘殺手足兇手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJzPCRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJzPCRN.jpg&h=f8ccc6b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"618bdf641b4dd2563929a634851022e3653f97b3","tid":1802311,"uid":70264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:41:50.000Z","msg":"中國人竟然過洋節"},{"pid":"8023992ad2b3239fd449090deeedd8e5d9c9ac32","tid":1802311,"uid":211941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"618bdf641b4dd2563929a634851022e3653f97b3","tid":1802311,"uid":70264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:41:50.000Z","msg":"中國人竟然過洋節"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:04:50.000Z","msg":"强调谴责中国駐港军人跳舞兴祝圣诞节，此行为严重伤害全国人民的感情！咱们是中国人不过八国联军的节日！这亦意味着驻港军队间接支持港独、颠覆国家政权！全国人民都不能够接受！<br />\n<